refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
resourcegmp_init mixednumber intbase0
Creates a GMP number from an integer or string.

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     5.3.2

      The base was extended from 2 to 36, to
      2 to 62 and -2 to -36.




     4.1.0

      The optional base parameter was added.

&reftitle.notes;



  To use the extended base introduced in PHP 5.3.2, then 
  PHP must be compiled against GMP 4.2.0 or greater.
